articles.title: Candace Owens Blocked From Entering Australia - Newsweek
articles.description: "Australia's national interest is best served when Candace Owens is somewhere else," said Minister of Home Affairs Tony Burke.
articles.content:
Commentator Candace Owens has reportedly been blocked from entering Australia ahead of a planned speaking tour.
